snippet.title: 2:05:23 Dude Quest 100%
snippet.description:
Every dude obtained, my dream from when I was a babyer person completed. An okay run, wasted a fair amount of time and didnt have the best luck (the weakest voodox ever witnessed lmao), but Cthude fight went well, poraque chomp will probably be obtained earlier in the future.  

Shoutouts to Loren, they patched the game several times to get C'thudes event working, by extension also fixing hellscream who was locked behind it.   -- Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/prismlx
